# ovh_vps_snapshot

Manages snapshot creation for an OVHcloud VPS.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/resources/vps_snapshot/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

The following arguments are supported:

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your VPS.
* `description` - (Optional) Description for the snapshot.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/resources/vps_snapshot.md for the full attribute list.)

The following attributes are exported:

* `id` - The ID of the snapshot.
* `creation_date` - Date when the snapshot was created.
* `description` - Description of the snapshot.
